## Step 11 — Browser Verification Checklist

- [ ] Go to the sign-up page, create a new account -> should redirect to /dashboard
- [ ] Refresh the page -> should still be logged in (session persists)
- [ ] Click Logout -> should redirect to the landing page (/)
- [ ] Access /dashboard directly without logging in -> should redirect to /login

