## Environment Variables Reminder (Part 7)

Make sure .env is never committed to Git. Your .gitignore should include:
```
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
```

All Vite env vars must be prefixed with VITE_:
```env
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://guouslhlbliprrigkytt.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here
```

